      <title><![CDATA[Introduction1]]></title>
      <descriptionText><![CDATA[<Introtext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:16pt; font-weight:bold; color:#cc0033; margin:10px; padding:0 0 0 5px; background:#e8e8e8; border-bottom:1px solid #333; display:block;">Welcome</Introtext><welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px">Welcome to the <i>Otsuka Sales Accelerator Simulation.</i><br><br>In this follow-up round of the simulation you will have a chance to practice the strategies you’ve learned for asking customers questions that help advance the prescribing cycle.<BR><BR>You will be applying the ROPE questioning model you learned:<BR><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Results</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Options</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Problems</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Execute Next Steps</li><BR>On each screen, you’ll choose from a set of possible questions and decide which is the best one to ask at that point in the conversation.<BR><BR>Each of the possible questions you consider has been rated according to the following individual metrics. Your score will reflect whether your decision making is in line with these characteristics.<BR><BR><b>Scoring Metrics:</b><BR><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Customer’s Needs</span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Decisions will help you better understand your customers’ treatment goals for their patients</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Decisions will capture new opportunities for the customer</li><br><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Sales Progress</span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Decisions build on previous discussions and align with where the customer is in their <span style="margin:0 0 0 16px;">prescribing cycle</span></li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Decisions advance the sale by "closing" at multiple points in the prescribing cycle<BR><BR><span style="color:#3366cc; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Trusted Advisor Relationship </span><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Decisions demonstrate a deep understanding of the customer's priorities and goals</li><li style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; color:#333; list-style-type:disc;">Decisions genuinely engage the customer by partnering with the customer to create value</welcomeText><lasttext style="font-family:Helvetica; font-size:11pt; color:#000; background-color:#c0c0c0; margin:10px; padding:2px 0 2px 5px; display:block;"><i>Please tap <b>Continue</b> or swipe to see information about you and your customer.</i></lasttext><welcomeText style=" font-family:Helvetica; font-size:12pt; line-height:18pt; text-align:justify; font-weight:normal; color:#333; display:block; margin:0 10px 10px"><BR><BR><I><B>Simulation Version: January 2012   0711T-3576E</B></I></welcomeText>]]></descriptionText>
